                    </div>
                    <span>The author of Getting the Most from Your Yellow Pages Advertising covers the subject completely, but he also offers tremendous insight into what it takes to advertise and promote your business in general. Even if you think you know all there is to know, you will find this an extremely valuable tool for your business!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A must buy for small business people.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
                      <span>0</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>1998-09-25</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>For those of us who are spending significant money each and every single month on yellow pages advertising, this book is a godsend. It explains what really works and what doesn't, which directories to advertise in and which to avoid, and above all how to make your ads work as well as they possibly can.<P>Beyond that it's humorous and extremely entertaining.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">I've worked with the author. Highly recommended.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
