                    <span>I've worked with Barry Maher, the author of the book, and there's a reason TIME magazine called him the best in the business.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Why has Amazon removed the names and emails of reviewers</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
